          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-1" n="1">An ass's hoof alone can hold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-2" n="2">That poisonous juice which kills by cold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-3" n="3">Methought, when I this poem read,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-4" n="4">No vessel but an ass's head,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-5" n="5">Such frigid fustian could contain;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-6" n="6">I mean the head without the brain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-7" n="7">The cold conceits, the chilling thoughts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-8" n="8">Went down like stupefying draughts:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-9" n="9">I found my head began to swim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-10" n="10">A numbness crept through every limb:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-11" n="11">In haste, with imprecations dire,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-12" n="12">I threw the volume in the fire:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-13" n="13">When, who could think, though cold as ice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-14" n="14">It burnt to ashes in a trice.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-15" n="15"><lb/>How could I more enhance its fame?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-ROGP-line-16" n="16">Though born in snow, it died in flame.</l>
          </lg>
